  "description": "The cloud preset. Thin, wispy, barely there — sawSpread at 0.1, no sub oscillator, mostly shimmer tail at 0.5 mix with high feedback at 0.7. The dry signal is a ghost; the wet signal is the atmosphere. The Guru says: sometimes the instrument is the reverb. The oscillator is just the excuse.",
